description:
When the sun rides low on the horizon, pull on a Better Sweater and stay warm – and stay out a little longer. With a knit outer face and an easy-care fleece interior, it functions as a superb insulating piece in the backcountry or around home. The deep neck keeps heat inside, and the low-impact dyes keep its eco-footprint small.Polyester heavy-weight fleece has sweater-knit face, and a soft brushed interior.Dyed by a low-impact process that keeps the use of dyestuffs, energy, and water to a minimum.1/4 zip neck with stand up collar.Raglan sleeves are comfortable under backpack straps.Princess seams at back add shaping.Zippered sleeve pocket.

        Sustainability






